    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine starts reliably and the transmission shifts smoothly, offering a dependable driving experience. While the exterior is generally clean, there are a few minor surface scratches and light wear consistent with its age. Inside, the cabin is tidy and the upholstery is in good shape, though there is some slight fading on the dashboard. All major features and electronics are fully functional, making this a solid choice for anyone looking for a reliable and well-cared-for vehicle.",
