    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of exceptional caliber, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This specimen exhibits an immaculate aesthetic and mechanical profile, representing the pinnacle of its class. Every detail has been scrutinized to ensure a showroom-quality experience for the discerning collector. We invite you to acquire a vehicle that transcends the standard pre-owned market.",
