      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't find another one like this. It's been my absolute pride and joy, kept in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washed every single weekend. It looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I'm only letting it go because I'm moving, so my loss is your gain. This beauty is in truly flawless shape\u2014not a scratch or a ding to be found. Come take a look, you're going to fall in love with how it drives!",
      "price": 43500.0,
