      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L atmospheric inline-six. This example is mechanically impeccable, featuring documented rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive high-pressure VANOS overhaul. The rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to mitigate common chassis fatigue, ensuring structural rigidity. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with fresh OEM bushings and dampers, providing the signature tactile feedback and lateral grip expected of this chassis. No deferred maintenance; a turn-key investment for the enthusiast who demands technical perfection.",
